data.description:
This spacious 2-story country home sits on 30 acres with several ponds. The home features 2,180 heated sqft. of living space, 2 car attached garage with 4 beds and 2 baths, and two living rooms, perfect for a growing family. Utilize the backyard and 30 acres as a garden or play area and two ponds for fishing and amazing hunting. Embrace your creativity and transform the cellar basement into a game room, 2nd living room, or even a cozy wine cellar, a detached outbuilding that offers the potential for a workshop or extra storage space.
This property is all kinds of secluded, and the house sits on a fill side. The house is a couple of miles from Wister Lake Dam for boaters and fishing. While this property has a lot to offer, it also presents an opportunity for those looking to add their personal touch. With a few improvements, you can transform this splendid property into a haven that truly reflects your style and taste. This home is priced to sell, so don't miss out on this opportunity!
